OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FThe government's widely anticipated,
OL,7,Fand long-delayed, Schools White Paper
OL,8,Fis set to be published in full on
OL,9,FMonday after months of speculation.
OL,11,FIt comes after details of special
OL,12,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,13,F(SEND) reforms, one part of the White
OL,14,FPaper, were leaked on Thursday,
OL,15,Fcausing panic among some charities and
OL,16,Fparents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
