CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FThe government is expected to focus on
OL,7,Fmaking mainstream schools more
OL,8,Finclusive, signalling a shift away
OL,9,Ffrom a model which has seen a growing
OL,10,Fnumber of children attend expensive
OL,11,Fspecialist schools.
OL,13,FThe Schools White Paper was originally
OL,14,Fset to be published in autumn 2025,
OL,15,Fbut was delayed to allow a further
OL,16,Fperiod to test SEND reforms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FMainstream schools will receive direct
OL,7,Ffunding to support SEND children as
OL,8,Fpart of a #4 billion package, set to
OL,9,Fbe announced on Monday, to make the
OL,10,Fsystem more inclusive, including
OL,11,Finvestment in training for adaptive
OL,12,Fteaching styles.
OL,14,FSome #1.6 billion over three years
OL,15,Fwill be provided to early years,
OL,16,Fschools and colleges through an
OL,17,F"inclusive mainstream fund".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FWhile another #1.8 billion over the
OL,7,Fsame period will go towards creating
OL,8,Fan "experts at hand" service, made up
OL,9,Fof specialists such as SEND teachers
OL,10,Fand speech and language therapists in
OL,11,Fevery area.
OL,13,FThe White Paper will set out to change
OL,14,Fthe current legal rights of children
OL,15,Fwith less severe needs, and instead
OL,16,Festablish a new tiered structure for
OL,17,Fsupporting SEND children, based on the
OL,18,Flevel of their need.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
