OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FITV News understands that as part of
OL,7,Fthis education, health and care plans
OL,8,F(EHCPs), a legal document that details
OL,9,Fchildren's support, will be reassessed
OL,10,Fonce children reach the end of primary
OL,11,Fschool.
OL,13,FThe reforms are expected to introduce
OL,14,Fa plan with legal footing for all
OL,15,Fchildren with SEND called Individual
OL,16,FSupport Plans (ISPs) and it is
OL,17,Funderstood they will apply to children
OL,18,Fwho have assessed as needing
OL,19,Fspecialist support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FITV News understands that the changes
OL,7,Fwill come into force in 2030 to give
OL,8,Fmainstream schools time to prepare to
OL,9,Fsupport more children with additional
OL,10,Fneeds.
OL,12,FMarsha Martin, who runs the group
OL,13,FBlack SEN Mamas, a support network for
OL,14,FBlack mothers of SEND children, is
OL,15,Fworried about changes to EHCPs.
OL,17,FMs Martin, who is neurodivergent
OL,18,Fherself and has three daughters who
OL,19,Fall have additional needs, said she
OL,20,Ffears the reforms could erode both
OL,21,Fchildren's and parents' legal rights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,F"It almost seems as though what they
OL,7,Fare putting in place might stand to
OL,8,Fexacerbate the issues that we
OL,9,Fcurrently have," she told ITV News.
OL,11,F"All we have actually asked for is
OL,12,Fthat there is better adherence to the
OL,13,Flaws by local authority and that local
OL,14,Fauthorities are held to account and
OL,15,Fthat there is a push to moving towards
OL,16,Fwhat SEND inclusion looks like."
OL,18,FMarsha Martin, who runs the group
OL,19,FBlack SEN Mamas, spoke to ITV News
OL,20,Fabout her concerns over the leaked
OL,21,Fgovernment SEND reforms
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
