OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,F"It almost seems as though what they
OL,7,Fare putting in place might stand to
OL,8,Fexacerbate the issues that we
OL,9,Fcurrently have," she told ITV News.
OL,11,F"All we have actually asked for is
OL,12,Fthat there is better adherence to the
OL,13,Flaws by local authority and that local
OL,14,Fauthorities are held to account and
OL,15,Fthat there is a push to moving towards
OL,16,Fwhat SEND inclusion looks like."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
