FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FThe National Association of
OL,7,FHeadteachers (NAHT) welcomed the
OL,8,F"principle" of more support for pupils
OL,9,Fin mainstream schools, but added
OL,10,F"along with this significant
OL,11,Finvestment, we will be scrutinising
OL,12,Fthe details closely and speaking to
OL,13,Fschool leaders to weigh up whether it
OL,14,Fis sufficient".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]rD@AOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,7,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, said:
OL,8,F"There will always be some pupils
OL,9,Fwhose needs are so great that they
OL,10,Frequire support in a special school,
OL,11,Fand it's crucial the government's
OL,12,Fplans ensure all children get the
OL,13,Fsupport they need at the right time in
OL,14,Fthe right setting."
OL,16,FWhat can we expect from the Schools
OL,17,FWhite Paper?
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FAlongside reforms to the SEND system,
OL,7,Fthe government is expected to set out
OL,8,Fnew programmes to tackle the
OL,9,Fachievement gap between pupils from
OL,10,Fpoorer backgrounds compared with their
OL,11,Fmore affluent peers, including in
OL,12,Fareas in the North of England.
OL,14,FThe two new programmes, Mission North
OL,15,FEast and Mission Coastal, will aim to
OL,16,Ftackle poorer performance for
OL,17,Fdisadvantaged pupils in the areas,
OL,18,Fincluding working-class pupils.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FIt will be based on the model of the
OL,7,FLondon Challenge, a programme which
OL,8,Fwas introduced to improve schools in
OL,9,FLondon under the Labour government in
OL,10,F2003.
OL,12,FThe government will also set a new
OL,13,Ftarget for attendance to recover 20
OL,14,Fmillion school days a year by the end
OL,15,Fof 2028/29 compared with 2023/24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FInstead of targeting disadvantage
OL,7,Ffunding based on whether a child is
OL,8,Feligible to receive free school meals,
OL,9,Fafter a consultation, distribution of
OL,10,Ffunding to schools could take into
OL,11,Faccount how low family income is, how
OL,12,Flong this has been the case, and the
OL,13,Fplace a child lives.
OL,15,FThe government hopes it will remove
OL,16,Fthe need for families to choose to
OL,17,Ftake up free school meals to be
OL,18,Feligible for deprivation funding, in
OL,19,Fan attempt to cut admin for schools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FThe White Paper will also set out how
OL,7,Fincentives worth up to #15,000 will be
OL,8,Foffered to newly appointed
OL,9,Fheadteachers to work in parts of the
OL,10,Fcountry that need heads.
OL,12,FIt will further include a commitment
OL,13,Fto develop minimum expectations for
OL,14,Fschools around how they communicate
OL,15,Fwith parents and manage pupils'
OL,16,Ftransition from primary to secondary
OL,17,Fschool.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fpromised "tailored support" for
OL,8,Ffamilies and an end to the "one size
OL,9,Ffits all system".
OL,11,FMeanwhile the Education Secretary said
OL,12,Fthe government was "fiercely ambitious
OL,13,Ffor children and young people with
OL,14,FSEND", who deserve a system that
OL,15,F"lifts them up, and that puts no limit
OL,16,Fon what they can go on to achieve".
