PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1771909410
OL,3,CSEND reform: Delayed government
OL,4,CSchools White Paper to be published
OL,6,FSpeaking on Sunday, ahead of the
OL,7,Fofficial publication of the White
OL,8,FPaper, Bridget Phillipson said:"These
OL,9,Freforms are a watershed moment for a
OL,10,Fgeneration of young people and
OL,11,Fgenerations to come, and a major
OL,12,Fmilestone in this government's mission
OL,13,Fto make sure opportunity is for each
OL,14,Fand every child."
